  "detailed_description": "<strong>Everglow</strong> is a sci-fi visual novel about the space adventures of the fox <strong>Glow</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/7b7f3e09d70a8fb874888421e10e8400.poster.avif?t=1704959613\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/7b7f3e09d70a8fb874888421e10e8400.webm?t=1704959613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/7b7f3e09d70a8fb874888421e10e8400.mp4?t=1704959613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Ten years ago, an incident occurred that sowed discord between the empires of Wolves and Foxes. But it doesn't matter to <strong>Glow</strong>, an ordinary and unremarkable employee of the research institute. Her days are devoted to shuffling papers around at work and talking with her beloved cactus at home. But soon, everything will change...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/17e4d6ae85dc0138d01fd8338f052774.poster.avif?t=1704959613\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/17e4d6ae85dc0138d01fd8338f052774.webm?t=1704959613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/17e4d6ae85dc0138d01fd8338f052774.mp4?t=1704959613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > How deep is the fox hole? </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unravel a government conspiracy or become part of it.<br></li><li> Discover all 5 unique endings.<br></li><li> Be the fox you've always wanted to be.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Everglow</strong> is a sci-fi visual novel about the space adventures of the fox <strong>Glow</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/7b7f3e09d70a8fb874888421e10e8400.poster.avif?t=1704959613\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/7b7f3e09d70a8fb874888421e10e8400.webm?t=1704959613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/7b7f3e09d70a8fb874888421e10e8400.mp4?t=1704959613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Ten years ago, an incident occurred that sowed discord between the empires of Wolves and Foxes. But it doesn't matter to <strong>Glow</strong>, an ordinary and unremarkable employee of the research institute. Her days are devoted to shuffling papers around at work and talking with her beloved cactus at home. But soon, everything will change...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/17e4d6ae85dc0138d01fd8338f052774.poster.avif?t=1704959613\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/17e4d6ae85dc0138d01fd8338f052774.webm?t=1704959613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763150/extras/17e4d6ae85dc0138d01fd8338f052774.mp4?t=1704959613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > How deep is the fox hole? </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unravel a government conspiracy or become part of it.<br></li><li> Discover all 5 unique endings.<br></li><li> Be the fox you've always wanted to be.</li></ul>",
